name: Froggity Frog
description:
Description

Game made in around  10 hours of work for Mini Game Jam 79: Frog

Programmed by one person. Most pixel art was made by me as well besides the background. Most audio is from online sources.

This was a lot of fun, needed a chill small project to get back to programming, so here it is.

Hope you enjoy!

Assets used:

Background: https://opengameart.org/content/background-5

Font: https://www.1001fonts.com/kongtext-font.html
